Native clang stage0 @LLVM_VERSION@.

This prefix is a bootstrap package for building final target clang packages.
It is built for @HOST_TRIPLE@ and uses the same-version host llvmsdk as the
installed LLVM provider.

Bootstrap compiler LLVM version: @BOOTSTRAP_LLVM_VERSION@
Stage0 LLVM targets: @STAGE0_TARGETS@

Included projects:
  clang
  lld
